  "title": "🚀 Business Development Executive (Entry-Level / Fresh Graduates Welcome)",
  "description": "<h2>🚀 <strong>Business Development Executive (Entry-Level / Fresh Graduates Welcome)</strong></h2><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Central <br />🕘 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours<br />💼 <strong>Salary:</strong> 3600-3900 + Performance Incentives</p><h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3><p>We are looking for <strong>motivated and driven individuals</strong> to join our team as <strong>Business Development Executives</strong>. This role focuses on identifying new business opportunities, building client relationships, and supporting company growth.<br />No prior experience is required — <strong>training will be provided</strong>, making this a great opportunity for fresh graduates who are keen to start a career in business development and sales.<br /></p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Identify and approach potential clients through calls, emails, and networking</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong relationships with new and existing clients</p></li><li><p>Understand client needs and recommend suitable products or services</p></li><li><p>Prepare basic proposals, quotations, or presentations</p></li><li><p>Conduct market research to identify new business opportunities</p></li><li><p>Work closely with internal teams to support business growth targets<br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Business, Marketing, Finance, or related fields</p></li><li><p>Entry-level candidates and fresh graduates are welcome</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills<br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Structured training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Clear career progression path</p></li><li><p>Exposure to sales, marketing, and strategy</p></li><li><p>Supportive and dynamic work environment</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives<br /></p><p>R25156061</p><p>Just Recruit Singapore Pte Ltd - EA12C6295</p></li></ul>",
